<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>남산 남사면 협업 설계 워크샵 — Namsan South Slope Workshop</title>
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=DM+Serif+Display:ital@0;1&family=Noto+Sans+KR:wght@300;400;500;700&family=JetBrains+Mono:wght@400&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
*{margin:0;padding:0;box-sizing:border-box}
:root{
  --bg:#FAF8F4;--bg2:#F0EDE6;--bg3:#E8E4DC;
  --tx:#1A1A1A;--tx2:#4A4A4A;--tx3:#8A8A8A;
  --team-a:#D63B3A;--team-b:#C4501E;--team-c:#A66A10;
  --team-d:#0D7A5F;--team-e:#4A3FA5;
  --serif:'DM Serif Display',Georgia,serif;
  --sans:'Noto Sans KR','Helvetica Neue',sans-serif;
  --mono:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;
}
html{scroll-behavior:smooth}
body{background:var(--bg);color:var(--tx);font-family:var(--sans);font-weight:400;line-height:1.7;-webkit-font-smoothing:antialiased}

/* Language toggle */
.lang-toggle{position:fixed;top:20px;right:20px;z-index:100;display:flex;border:1px solid var(--tx);border-radius:2px;overflow:hidden;font-size:12px;letter-spacing:.05em;backdrop-filter:blur(12px)}
.lang-btn{padding:6px 14px;cursor:pointer;background:transparent;color:var(--tx);transition:all .2s;font-family:var(--mono);border:none;font-size:12px}
.lang-btn.active{background:var(--tx);color:var(--bg)}
.hero-area .lang-toggle{border-color:rgba(255,255,255,.4)}
.hero-area .lang-btn{color:rgba(255,255,255,.7)}
.hero-area .lang-btn.active{background:rgba(255,255,255,.9);color:#1A1A1A}

/* Hero */
.hero{background:#1A1E2E;color:#fff;min-height:100vh;display:flex;flex-direction:column;justify-content:center;padding:80px 40px 60px;position:relative;overflow:hidden}
.hero::before{content:'';position:absolute;top:0;left:0;right:0;bottom:0;background:linear-gradient(135deg,rgba(26,30,46,.95),rgba(26,30,46,.7));z-index:1}
.hero>*{position:relative;z-index:2}
.hero-label{font-family:var(--mono);font-size:11px;letter-spacing:.15em;color:rgba(255,255,255,.4);margin-bottom:24px;text-transform:uppercase}
.hero h1{font-family:var(--serif);font-size:clamp(36px,6vw,64px);font-weight:400;line-height:1.15;margin-bottom:16px;max-width:700px}
.hero h1 em{font-style:italic;color:rgba(255,255,255,.5)}
.hero-sub{font-size:15px;color:rgba(255,255,255,.45);max-width:550px;line-height:1.8;margin-bottom:48px}
.hero-teams{display:flex;gap:16px;flex-wrap:wrap}
.hero-team{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;font-size:12px;color:rgba(255,255,255,.5);font-family:var(--mono)}
.hero-team .dot{width:10px;height:10px;border-radius:50%}
.scroll-hint{position:absolute;bottom:30px;left:50%;transform:translateX(-50%);z-index:2;font-size:11px;color:rgba(255,255,255,.25);letter-spacing:.1em;font-family:var(--mono);animation:float 2s ease-in-out infinite}
@keyframes float{0%,100%{transform:translateX(-50%) translateY(0)}50%{transform:translateX(-50%) translateY(-6px)}}

/* Map section */
.map-section{padding:80px 40px;background:#1A1E2E}
.map-section h2{font-family:var(--serif);font-size:28px;color:#fff;margin-bottom:6px}
.map-section .sub{font-size:13px;color:rgba(255,255,255,.35);margin-bottom:32px;font-family:var(--mono)}
.map-wrap{max-width:900px;margin:0 auto;display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:40px;align-items:start}
.map-img{width:100%;border-radius:8px;border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.08)}
.map-legend{display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:12px}
.legend-item{display:flex;align-items:flex-start;gap:12px;padding:14px 16px;background:rgba(255,255,255,.04);border-left:3px solid;border-radius:0 6px 6px 0;transition:background .2s}
.legend-item:hover{background:rgba(255,255,255,.08)}
.legend-item h4{font-size:13px;color:#fff;font-weight:500;margin-bottom:2px}
.legend-item p{font-size:11px;color:rgba(255,255,255,.4);line-height:1.5}
.legend-item .spots{font-size:10px;color:rgba(255,255,255,.25);font-family:var(--mono);margin-top:4px}

/* Content */
.content{max-width:900px;margin:0 auto;padding:80px 40px}
.section-label{font-family:var(--mono);font-size:11px;letter-spacing:.15em;color:var(--tx3);margin-bottom:32px;text-transform:uppercase}

/* Team card */
.team-card{margin-bottom:64px;border-top:1px solid var(--bg3);padding-top:40px}
.team-header{display:flex;align-items:baseline;gap:16px;margin-bottom:8px;flex-wrap:wrap}
.team-badge{font-family:var(--mono);font-size:11px;letter-spacing:.08em;color:#fff;padding:3px 10px;border-radius:2px}
.team-title-kr{font-family:var(--serif);font-size:28px}
.team-title-en{font-size:14px;color:var(--tx3);font-style:italic;margin-bottom:24px}
.team-spots{font-size:12px;color:var(--tx3);margin-bottom:28px;padding:10px 14px;background:var(--bg2);border-radius:4px;line-height:1.8}

.two-col{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:32px;margin-bottom:24px}
.col-label{font-family:var(--mono);font-size:10px;letter-spacing:.12em;text-transform:uppercase;margin-bottom:12px;padding-bottom:6px;border-bottom:1px solid var(--bg3)}
.issue-kr{font-size:14px;color:var(--tx);line-height:1.8;margin-bottom:12px}
.issue-en{font-size:13px;color:var(--tx3);line-height:1.8;font-style:italic}

.question-list{display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:12px}
.q-item{padding:14px 16px;background:var(--bg2);border-radius:4px;position:relative}
.q-num{font-family:var(--mono);font-size:11px;position:absolute;top:14px;left:16px}
.q-kr{font-size:13px;margin-left:28px;margin-bottom:4px;line-height:1.7}
.q-en{font-size:12px;color:var(--tx3);margin-left:28px;font-style:italic;line-height:1.6}

.refs{font-size:11px;color:var(--tx3);font-family:var(--mono);padding-top:16px;border-top:1px solid var(--bg3);letter-spacing:.01em}

/* Connections section */
.connections{margin-bottom:64px;border-top:1px solid var(--bg3);padding-top:40px}
.connections h3{font-family:var(--serif);font-size:24px;margin-bottom:6px}
.connections .sub{font-size:13px;color:var(--tx3);font-style:italic;margin-bottom:28px}
.conn-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(250px,1fr));gap:12px}
.conn-item{padding:16px;background:var(--bg2);border-radius:4px;border-left:3px solid var(--bg3)}
.conn-item .kr{font-size:13px;margin-bottom:4px}
.conn-item .en{font-size:12px;color:var(--tx3);font-style:italic}
.conn-item .link{font-size:10px;color:var(--tx3);font-family:var(--mono);margin-top:6px}

/* Footer */
footer{background:#1A1E2E;color:rgba(255,255,255,.3);padding:40px;text-align:center;font-size:12px;line-height:1.8}
footer a{color:rgba(255,255,255,.5)}

/* Language switching */
[data-lang="en"]{display:none}
body.en [data-lang="ko"]{display:none}
body.en [data-lang="en"]{display:block}
body.en [data-lang="en-inline"]{display:inline}
body.en [data-lang="ko-inline"]{display:none}
[data-lang="en-inline"]{display:none}

/* Mobile */
@media(max-width:768px){
  .hero{padding:60px 24px 40px}
  .map-wrap{grid-template-columns:1fr}
  .two-col{grid-template-columns:1fr}
  .content{padding:48px 24px}
  .map-section{padding:48px 24px}
  .conn-grid{grid-template-columns:1fr}
  .lang-toggle{top:12px;right:12px}
}

/* Print */
@media print{
  .lang-toggle,.scroll-hint{display:none}
  .hero{min-height:auto;padding:40px;page-break-after:always}
  .team-card{page-break-inside:avoid}
}
</style>
</head>
<body>

<!-- Language Toggle -->
<div class="lang-toggle hero-area" id="langToggle">
  <button class="lang-btn active" onclick="setLang('ko')">KO</button>
  <button class="lang-btn" onclick="setLang('en')">EN</button>
</div>

<!-- Hero -->
<section class="hero">
  <div class="hero-label">Collaborative Urban Design Workshop — Vienna 2026</div>
  <h1>
    <span data-lang="ko">남산 남사면<br>협업 설계 워크샵</span>
    <span data-lang="en">Namsan South Slope<br><em>Collaborative Design</em></span>
  </h1>
  <p class="hero-sub">
    <span data-lang="ko">용산구 후암동 · 해방촌 · 이태원2동 · 한남동 경계<br>5개 팀 × 7개 설계 스팟 — 남산 남사면 전체를 하나의 시스템으로</span>
    <span data-lang="en">Yongsan-gu: Huam-dong · Haebangchon · Itaewon 2-dong · Hannam boundary<br>5 teams × 7 design spots — the entire south slope as one interconnected system</span>
  </p>
  <div class="hero-teams">
    <div class="hero-team"><div class="dot" style="background:var(--team-a)"></div>Team A</div>
    <div class="hero-team"><div class="dot" style="background:var(--team-b)"></div>Team B</div>
    <div class="hero-team"><div class="dot" style="background:var(--team-c)"></div>Team C</div>
    <div class="hero-team"><div class="dot" style="background:var(--team-d)"></div>Team D</div>
    <div class="hero-team"><div class="dot" style="background:var(--team-e)"></div>Team E</div>
  </div>
  <div class="scroll-hint">↓ SCROLL</div>
</section>

<!-- Map -->
<section class="map-section">
  <h2>
    <span data-lang="ko">답사 루트 · 설계 스팟</span>
    <span data-lang="en">Field Route · Design Spots</span>
  </h2>
  <div class="sub">7 spots across the Namsan south slope</div>
  <div class="map-wrap">
    <img src="map_annotated.png" alt="Annotated map of Namsan south slope with 7 design spots" class="map-img">
    <div class="map-legend">
      <div class="legend-item" style="border-color:var(--team-a)">
        <div>
          <h4>Team A — <span data-lang="ko-inline">경사지 보행</span><span data-lang="en-inline">Hillside Mobility</span></h4>
          <p data-lang="ko">108계단 경사형 승강기 + 한남·하얏트 경계부의 수직 접근성 문제</p>
          <p data-lang="en">Vertical accessibility at the 108 Stairs inclined elevator and the Hannam/Hyatt boundary</p>
          <div class="spots">Spot 1 + Spot 6</div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="legend-item" style="border-color:var(--team-b)">
        <div>
          <h4>Team B — <span data-lang="ko-inline">도시재생 vs 젠트리피케이션</span><span data-lang="en-inline">Regeneration vs Gentrification</span></h4>
          <p data-lang="ko">해방촌 오거리·신흥시장 — 공공 재생이 촉발한 상업화의 역설</p>
          <p data-lang="en">Haebangchon 5-way & Sinheung Market — the paradox of public-led regeneration</p>
          <div class="spots">Spot 2</div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="legend-item" style="border-color:var(--team-c)">
        <div>
          <h4>Team C — <span data-lang="ko-inline">경사지 주거정비</span><span data-lang="en-inline">Housing Renewal on Slopes</span></h4>
          <p data-lang="ko">후암동 노후주거지 — 특별계획구역 내 전면 철거 vs 점진적 재생</p>
          <p data-lang="en">Huam-dong deteriorated housing — total demolition vs incremental regeneration</p>
          <div class="spots">Spot 3</div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="legend-item" style="border-color:var(--team-d)">
        <div>
          <h4>Team D — <span data-lang="ko-inline">녹지축 · 생태경계</span><span data-lang="en-inline">Green Axis + Ecological Boundary</span></h4>
          <p data-lang="ko">남산 그린웨이 축 + 소월길 13m 옹벽 — 단절된 생태축 복원</p>
          <p data-lang="en">Namsan Greenway axis + Sowol-gil 13m retaining wall — restoring the severed green corridor</p>
          <div class="spots">Spot 4 + Spot 7</div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="legend-item" style="border-color:var(--team-e)">
        <div>
          <h4>Team E — <span data-lang="ko-inline">가로 활력 · 용도 전환</span><span data-lang="en-inline">Street Vitality + Use Transition</span></h4>
          <p data-lang="ko">이태원2동·디지텍고 일대 — 코로나 이후 상권 위축과 빈 점포</p>
          <p data-lang="en">Itaewon 2-dong area — post-COVID commercial decline and vacant storefronts</p>
          <div class="spots">Spot 5</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- Team Details -->
<div class="content">
  <div class="section-label">
    <span data-lang="ko">팀별 설계 브리프</span>
    <span data-lang="en">Team Design Briefs</span>
  </div>

  <!-- Team A -->
  <div class="team-card">
    <div class="team-header">
      <span class="team-badge" style="background:var(--team-a)">TEAM A</span>
      <span class="team-title-kr" data-lang="ko">경사지 보행</span>
      <span class="team-title-kr" data-lang="en">Hillside Mobility</span>
    </div>
    <div class="team-title-en">
      <span data-lang="ko">Hillside Mobility</span>
      <span data-lang="en">경사지 보행</span>
    </div>
    <div class="team-spots">
      <span data-lang="ko">Spot 1 — 108계단 · 경사형 승강기 &nbsp;|&nbsp; Spot 6 — 한남 · 하얏트 경계</span>
      <span data-lang="en">Spot 1 — 108 Stairs + Inclined Elevator &nbsp;|&nbsp; Spot 6 — Hannam / Grand Hyatt Boundary</span>
    </div>
    <div class="two-col">
      <div>
        <div class="col-label" style="color:var(--team-a)">
          <span data-lang="ko">핵심 이슈 Core Issue</span>
          <span data-lang="en">Core Issue 핵심 이슈</span>
        </div>
        <div class="issue-kr" data-lang="ko">두 지점 모두 극심한 표고차(108계단: 53m 구간 / 한남 지하차도: 11m 낙차)로 보행 네트워크가 단절된 곳. 1943년 일제 신사 참배길이었던 108계단에는 2018년 서울 주택가 최초의 경사형 승강기(28억원)가 설치됨. 한남 경계부는 하얏트 슈퍼블록이 지역 가로 네트워크를 차단하는 전형적 사례.</div>
        <div class="issue-kr" data-lang="en">Both spots share extreme elevation gaps severing pedestrian networks. The 108 Stairs — originally a 1943 Japanese shrine path — received Seoul's first residential inclined elevator in 2018 (2.8B KRW). The Hannam boundary shows how the Hyatt superblock fragments the local street grid.</div>
      </div>
      <div>
        <div class="col-label" style="color:var(--team-a)">
          <span data-lang="ko">설계 질문 Design Questions</span>
          <span data-lang="en">Design Questions 설계 질문</span>
        </div>
        <div class="question-list">
          <div class="q-item"><div class="q-num" style="color:var(--team-a)">Q1</div><div class="q-kr" data-lang="ko">경사형 승강기 모델이 다른 구릉지 마을로 확장 가능한가, 아니면 단발성 개입인가?</div><div class="q-kr" data-lang="en">Can the inclined elevator model scale to other hillside neighborhoods, or is it a one-off intervention?</div></div>
          <div class="q-item"><div class="q-num" style="color:var(--team-a)">Q2</div><div class="q-kr" data-lang="ko">하얏트 슈퍼블록이 만든 가로 단절을 어떻게 재연결할 수 있는가?</div><div class="q-kr" data-lang="en">How would you reconnect the street grid fragmented by the Hyatt superblock?</div></div>
          <div class="q-item"><div class="q-num" style="color:var(--team-a)">Q3</div><div class="q-kr" data-lang="ko">차량 인프라와 보행자 우선 경사지 설계의 적정 균형점은?</div><div class="q-kr" data-lang="en">What is the right balance between vehicular infrastructure and pedestrian-first hillside design?</div></div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="refs">cf. Lisbon — Elevador da Bica &nbsp;|&nbsp; Medellín — Escaleras Eléctricas &nbsp;|&nbsp; Vienna — Strudlhofstiege</div>
  </div>

  <!-- Team B -->
  <div class="team-card">
    <div class="team-header">
      <span class="team-badge" style="background:var(--team-b)">TEAM B</span>
      <span class="team-title-kr" data-lang="ko">도시재생 vs 젠트리피케이션</span>
      <span class="team-title-kr" data-lang="en">Regeneration vs Gentrification</span>
    </div>
    <div class="team-title-en">
      <span data-lang="ko">Regeneration vs Gentrification</span>
      <span data-lang="en">도시재생 vs 젠트리피케이션</span>
    </div>
    <div class="team-spots">
      <span data-lang="ko">Spot 2 — 해방촌 오거리 · 신흥시장</span>
      <span data-lang="en">Spot 2 — Haebangchon 5-way Intersection & Sinheung Market</span>
    </div>
    <div class="two-col">
      <div>
        <div class="col-label" style="color:var(--team-b)">
          <span data-lang="ko">핵심 이슈 Core Issue</span>
          <span data-lang="en">Core Issue 핵심 이슈</span>
        </div>
        <div class="issue-kr" data-lang="ko">170억원 투입 도시재생(8대 마중물사업), 신흥시장 클라우드 지붕(2024 서울시 건축상 대상). 그러나 상가 월세 3배 폭등(2015년 50만→2018년 150만원). 2~3층 휴먼스케일은 유지되나, 원주민 상업·주거 이탈 가속. 상생협약(2016) 체결에도 실효성 논란.</div>
        <div class="issue-kr" data-lang="en">170B KRW public regeneration with 8 anchor projects; Sinheung Market's cloud canopy won the 2024 Seoul Architecture Award. Yet rents tripled (500K→1.5M KRW/month, 2015–2018). Human-scale 2–3 story fabric survives, but original residents/businesses are displaced. Mutual-benefit agreements (2016) face effectiveness questions.</div>
      </div>
      <div>
        <div class="col-label" style="color:var(--team-b)">
          <span data-lang="ko">설계 질문 Design Questions</span>
          <span data-lang="en">Design Questions 설계 질문</span>
        </div>
        <div class="question-list">
          <div class="q-item"><div class="q-num" style="color:var(--team-b)">Q1</div><div class="q-kr" data-lang="ko">공간설계(정책이 아닌)로 젠트리피케이션을 늦출 수 있는가?</div><div class="q-kr" data-lang="en">Can spatial design (not just policy) slow gentrification — e.g. mixed-use zoning, community land trusts?</div></div>
          <div class="q-item"><div class="q-num" style="color:var(--team-b)">Q2</div><div class="q-kr" data-lang="ko">시장의 '클라우드 지붕'이 관광 경험과 동네 기능 사이를 어떻게 매개해야 하는가?</div><div class="q-kr" data-lang="en">How should the 'cloud roof' mediate between curated tourist experience and neighborhood functions?</div></div>
          <div class="q-item"><div class="q-num" style="color:var(--team-b)">Q3</div><div class="q-kr" data-lang="ko">공공 재생 사업 종료 후의 자생적 운영 모델은?</div><div class="q-kr" data-lang="en">What does a post-regeneration stewardship model look like when public funding ends?</div></div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="refs">cf. Vienna — Brunnenmarkt Regeneration &nbsp;|&nbsp; Berlin — Kreuzberg Anti-displacement &nbsp;|&nbsp; Seoul — Seongsu Sangsaeng Agreement</div>
  </div>

  <!-- Team C -->
  <div class="team-card">
    <div class="team-header">
      <span class="team-badge" style="background:var(--team-c)">TEAM C</span>
      <span class="team-title-kr" data-lang="ko">경사지 주거정비</span>
      <span class="team-title-kr" data-lang="en">Housing Renewal on Slopes</span>
    </div>
    <div class="team-title-en">
      <span data-lang="ko">Housing Renewal on Slopes</span>
      <span data-lang="en">경사지 주거정비</span>
    </div>
    <div class="team-spots">
      <span data-lang="ko">Spot 3 — 후암동 노후주거지 (특별계획구역 2구역)</span>
      <span data-lang="en">Spot 3 — Huam-dong Deteriorated Housing Zone (Special Planning Zone #2)</span>
    </div>
    <div class="two-col">
      <div>
